1.0.2.name: wordpress/rss-2-post
1.0.2.description:
This plugin will add items from an rss feed to your blog. The items will show after the content on your single post. The will pull new content every time the page loads thus helping with Google Rank since you will have new content on your single post pages.

Enjoy! Gordon French
